# Backend lane (functions)

- For Cloudflare Pages/Workers/Fns patterns, auth wiring, CORS, D1/Queues/etc: use cloudflare-full-stack-integration.
- For deploy/config/CLI work: use wrangler (and cloudflare-deploy when publishing).
- For endpoint design changes (inputs, auth, secrets, webhooks): use security-reviewer before shipping.
- For tricky bugs/regressions: systematic-debugging; for behavior changes: test-driven-development; before done: verification-before-completion.
